   <div class="widget widget_section_listing" id="section_listing-10">
    <div class="wscontrol section-listing-control" id="section-listing-control-7">
     <div class="section-box alumni-friends-section landscape-image">
      <h2>
       <a href="https://exchange.uncc.edu/section/alumni-friends/" title="ALUMNI &amp; FRIENDS Archives">
        ALUMNI &amp; FRIENDS
       </a>
      </h2>
      <div class="story alumni-friends-section landscape-image listing post-15726 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-college-publications">
       <div class="image" style="background-image:url('https://exchange.uncc.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/14/2018/11/Kim-Graham-600x392.jpg')" title="Featured Image">
       </div>
       <!-- .image -->
       <div class="details">
        <h3>
         <a href="https://exchange.uncc.edu/mpa-alumna-named-executive-director-for-apartment-association/" title="MPA Alumna Named Executive Director For Apartment Association">
          MPA Alumna Named Executive Director For Apartment Association
         </a>
        </h3>
        <div class="byline">
         November 14, 2018 by
         <a href="https://exchange.uncc.edu/author/lrobers2/" title="Posts by Lynn Roberson">
          Lynn Roberson
         </a>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
         <div class="excerpt">
          The Greater Charlotte Apartment Association has named UNC Charlotte alumna Kim S. Graham as its new executive director. Graham earned a Master of Public Administration degree from UNC Charlotte and most recently served as senior vice president of outreach and fund development with The Housing Partnership, a Charlotte-based housing nonprofit corporation.
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- .description -->
       </div>
       <!-- .details -->
      </div>
      <!-- .post -->
      <div class="story alumni-friends-section landscape-image listing post-15726 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-college-publications">
       <div class="image" style="background-image:url('https://exchange.uncc.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/14/2018/11/Laura-Clark-Exchange-600x392.jpg')" title="Featured Image">
       </div>
       <!-- .image -->
       <div class="details">
        <h3>
         <a href="https://exchange.uncc.edu/psychology-alumna-named-head-of-united-way-of-central-carolinas/" title="Psychology Alumna Named Head Of United Way of Central Carolinas">
          Psychology Alumna Named Head Of United Way of Central Carolinas
         </a>
        </h3>
        <div class="byline">
         November 14, 2018 by
         <a href="https://exchange.uncc.edu/author/lrobers2/" title="Posts by Lynn Roberson">
          Lynn Roberson
         </a>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
         <div class="excerpt">
          UNC Charlotte psychology alumna Laura Clark has been named the head of the United Way of Central Carolinas, which announced her as its new president and chief executive officer effective September 7. Clark became the sixth leader in the organization’s 86-year history. She earned a master’s degree in clinical/community psychology from UNC Charlotte and a bachelor’s degree in psychology from Appalachian State University.
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- .description -->
       </div>
